comprehensive test suite. The tests (`tests/test_synthesis_architecture_registry.py`) pass successfully and cover registry completeness, field validation, affinity logic, and consistency with other modules.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [x] None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid and well-tested. The choice of `frozenset` for REQUIRED_* constants and the use of `ArchitectureId.__args__` for reflection are elegant touches that keep the registry maintainable.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-019@20260416t054258z-verify.md"}}
